---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Funding"
  description="Support Loudoun Nature Conservation Project - learn how we're funded and how you can support student-led environmental conservation in Loudoun County, Virginia."
>
  <div class="bg-paper border-b hairline py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="font-display italic text-clay text-lg mb-4">Support Our Work</p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-medium text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-ink">Funding</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-20 bg-paper-2">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-clay mb-5">How We're Funded</p>
        <p class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
          Loudoun Nature Conservation Project operates as a volunteer-driven 501(c)(3) nonprofit. Our operations are currently funded through community donations, grants, and partnerships with local parks and schools. As a student-led organization, we keep overhead minimal to maximize our direct environmental impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-paper border hairline p-8 sm:p-10">
        <h2 class="font-display font-medium text-2xl text-ink mb-4">Support LNCP</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-soft text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Your support helps fund cleanup supplies, research equipment, outreach materials, and branch operations across Loudoun County. Every contribution - large or small - directly supports our mission.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink-soft text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Donations are tax-deductible under Section 501(c)(3). For donation inquiries or grant partnerships, please contact us.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:directors@loudounnatureconservation.org?subject=Donation%20%2F%20Funding%20Inquiry"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-forest-900 text-paper text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-forest-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Contact About Funding
        </a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-clay mb-5">Partner With Us</p>
        <p class="text-ink-soft text-sm leading-relaxed">
          We partner with local parks, businesses, schools, and environmental organizations to expand our reach and impact. If you're interested in becoming an LNCP partner, we'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
